First Devops Testing
---------------------

creating auto deployment after git commit using jenkins

create 2 jobs at jenkins:
-------------------------
1. listening to git commits - when commit triggered pusing the updates to the production environment
2. if update the production environment suceessed - run web monitoring job to verify the production server is up after the content update

